me.tatarka.ipromise

Class Result<T,E extends java.lang.Exception>

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.tatarka.ipromise.Result<T,E>

  • public final class Result<T,E extends java.lang.Exception>
extends java.lang.Object
    An immutable result from a promise. The result can be of either type success, error, or canceled. This class uses checked exceptions to ensure safety when retrieving the result.
